---
type Article = {
    title: string;
    description: string;
    href: string;
    image?: string;
    dateLabel: string;
};

interface Props {
    articles?: Article[];
}

const { articles = [] } = Astro.props as Props;
---

<section class="editorial-archive" aria-labelledby="archive-title">
    <div class="archive-shell">
        <header class="archive-header">
            <div>
                <p class="section-code">Z ARCHIWUM</p>
                <h2 id="archive-title">Skutki decyzji zostają dłużej niż ich nagłówki.</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="archive-intro">
                <p>
                    W archiwum widać ciąg dalszy: kto zyskał dostęp, kto poniósł koszt
                    i które obietnice przetrwały kontakt z wykonaniem.
                </p>
                <a href="/blog">Przejdź do całego archiwum <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></a>
            </div>
        </header>

        <div class="archive-grid">
            {articles.map((article, index) => (
                <a
                    class="archive-card"
                    href={article.href}
                    data-track-home-article={`archive-${index + 1}`}
                >
                    <div class="card-media">
                        {article.image && (
                            <img src={article.image} alt="" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
                        )}
                        <span class="card-index">0{index + 1}</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-copy">
                        <time>{article.dateLabel}</time>
                        <h3>{article.title}</h3>
                        <p>{article.description}</p>
                        <span class="card-link">Otwórz materiał <b aria-hidden="true">↗</b></span>
                    </div>
                </a>
            ))}
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="manifesto">
        <div class="manifesto-grid" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="manifesto-orbit" aria-hidden="true"><i></i><i></i><i></i></div>
        <div class="manifesto-shell">
                <p class="section-code">JAK CZYTAMY WYDARZENIA</p>
            <div class="manifesto-layout">
                <h2>Nie przewidujemy przyszłości. Sprawdzamy warunki, w których jest tworzona.</h2>
                <div>
                    <p>
                        Duże słowa są punktem wyjścia, nie dowodem. Patrzymy na pieniądze,
                        infrastrukturę, terminy i ludzi odpowiedzialnych za wykonanie decyzji.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Pytamy, co rzeczywiście się zmienia, kto ponosi koszt oraz czyja perspektywa
                        została pominięta w oficjalnej wersji wydarzeń.
                    </p>
                    <div class="manifesto-actions">
                        <a class="manifesto-primary" href="/about">O metodzie</a>
                        <a href="/contact">Napisz do redakcji</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .editorial-archive {
        color: #12372d;
        background: #f1eee5;
    }

    .archive-shell {
        width: min(1180px, calc(100% - 4rem));
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: clamp(5rem, 10vw, 9rem) 0;
    }

    .archive-header {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.4fr) minmax(280px, 0.65fr);
        align-items: end;
        gap: clamp(2rem, 7vw, 7rem);
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .section-code {
        margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
        color: #72570c;
        font-family: "Archivo Variable", "Atkinson", sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.64rem;
        font-weight: 680;
        letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    }

    h2 {
        margin: 0;
        color: #0b2c23;
        font-family: "Archivo Variable", "Atkinson", sans-serif;
        font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 5.7vw, 5.55rem);
        font-variation-settings: "wdth" 94;
        font-weight: 560;
        letter-spacing: -0.055em;
        line-height: 0.96;
        text-wrap: balance;
    }

    .archive-intro p {
        margin: 0;
        color: #4f685f;
        font-size: 0.98rem;
        line-height: 1.55;
    }

    .archive-intro a {
        margin-top: 1.2rem;
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.6rem;
        color: #173e32;
        font-family: "Archivo Variable", "Atkinson", sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.72rem;
        font-weight: 680;
        letter-spacing: 0.06em;
        text-decoration: none;
        text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .archive-intro a span {
        color: #a5821f;
        transition: transform 160ms ease;
    }

    .archive-intro a:hover span,
    .archive-intro a:focus-visible span {
        transform: translateX(4px);
    }

    .archive-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(18, 55, 45, 0.18);
        border-left: 1px solid rgba(18, 55, 45, 0.18);
    }

    .archive-card {
        min-width: 0;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-rows: auto 1fr;
        border-right: 1px solid rgba(18, 55, 45, 0.18);
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(18, 55, 45, 0.18);
        color: inherit;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: background 180ms ease, transform 180ms ease;
    }

    .card-media {
        position: relative;
        aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
        overflow: hidden;
        background: #183e33;
    }

    .card-media::after {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent 50%, rgba(5, 30, 24, 0.48));
    }

    .card-media img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
        border-radius: 0;
        filter: saturate(0.84) contrast(1.04);
        transition: transform 520ms cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.7, 0.2, 1), filter 300ms ease;
    }

    .card-index {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0.8rem;
        left: 0.8rem;
        z-index: 1;
        min-width: 35px;
        min-height: 35px;
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;
        border: 1px solid rgba(245, 232, 178, 0.34);
        color: #f1e4ad;
        background: rgba(4, 32, 25, 0.62);
        font-family: "Archivo Variable", "Atkinson", sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.6rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        backdrop-filter: blur(7px);
    }

    .card-copy {
        padding: clamp(1.2rem, 2.6vw, 2rem);
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .card-copy time {
        color: #6f560b;
        font-family: "Archivo Variable", "Atkinson", sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.62rem;
        font-weight: 650;
        letter-spacing: 0.11em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .card-copy h3 {
        margin: 0.75rem 0 0;
        color: #0e3228;
        font-family: "Archivo Variable", "Atkinson", sans-serif;
        font-size: clamp(1.35rem, 2.2vw, 2rem);
        font-variation-settings: "wdth" 96;
        font-weight: 590;
        letter-spacing: -0.035em;
        line-height: 1.05;
        text-wrap: balance;
    }

    .card-copy p {
        margin: 0.9rem 0 0;
        overflow: hidden;
        color: #50695f;
        font-size: 0.82rem;
        line-height: 1.45;
        display: -webkit-box;
        -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
        -webkit-line-clamp: 3;
    }

    .card-link {
        margin-top: auto;
        padding-top: 1.2rem;
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.7rem;
        color: #173f33;
        font-family: "Archivo Variable", "Atkinson", sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.65rem;
        font-weight: 680;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .card-link b {
        color: #9c7b1d;
        font-size: 1rem;
        transition: transform 180ms ease;
    }

    .archive-card:hover,
    .archive-card:focus-visible {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.52);
        outline: none;
    }

    .archive-card:hover img,
    .archive-card:focus-visible img {
        transform: scale(1.035);
        filter: saturate(0.88) contrast(1.04);
    }

    .archive-card:hover .card-link b,
    .archive-card:focus-visible .card-link b {
        transform: translate(3px, -3px);
    }

    .manifesto {
        position: relative;
        isolation: isolate;
        overflow: hidden;
        color: #eee9dc;
        background:
            radial-gradient(circle at 78% 52%, rgba(48, 141, 108, 0.2), transparent 29%),
            linear-gradient(132deg, #08281f, #071d1a 60%, #0b2526);
    }

    .manifesto-grid {
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        z-index: -1;
        opacity: 0.22;
        background-image:
            linear-gradient(rgba(226, 215, 170, 0.09) 1px, transparent 1px),
            linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(226, 215, 170, 0.09) 1px, transparent 1px);
        background-size: 48px 48px;
        mask-image: radial-gradient(circle at 78% 50%, black, transparent 60%);
    }

    .manifesto-orbit {
        position: absolute;
        top: 50%;
        right: -7vw;
        width: min(45vw, 620px);
        aspect-ratio: 1;
        border: 1px solid rgba(221, 188, 74, 0.18);
        border-radius: 50%;
        transform: translateY(-50%);
    }

    .manifesto-orbit::before,
    .manifesto-orbit::after,
    .manifesto-orbit i {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        border: 1px solid rgba(224, 203, 123, 0.12);
        border-radius: 50%;
    }

    .manifesto-orbit::before { inset: 14%; }
    .manifesto-orbit::after { inset: 29%; }
    .manifesto-orbit i:nth-child(1) { inset: 44%; background: rgba(213, 178, 58, 0.35); box-shadow: 0 0 50px rgba(213, 178, 58, 0.26); }
    .manifesto-orbit i:nth-child(2) { width: 8px; height: 8px; top: 18%; left: 34%; background: #d8b441; box-shadow: 0 0 15px #d8b441; }
    .manifesto-orbit i:nth-child(3) { width: 6px; height: 6px; right: 16%; bottom: 28%; background: #65b095; box-shadow: 0 0 15px #65b095; }

    .manifesto-shell {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
        width: min(1180px, calc(100% - 4rem));
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: clamp(5.5rem, 11vw, 10rem) 0;
    }

    .manifesto .section-code {
        color: #d4af3b;
    }

    .manifesto-layout {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.35fr) minmax(280px, 0.7fr);
        align-items: end;
        gap: clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 8rem);
    }

    .manifesto h2 {
        max-width: 16ch;
        color: #f1ede3;
    }

    .manifesto-layout > div > p {
        margin: 0 0 1rem;
        color: rgba(237, 234, 218, 0.66);
        font-size: 0.98rem;
        line-height: 1.55;
    }

    .manifesto-actions {
        margin-top: 1.7rem;
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 0.7rem;
    }

    .manifesto-actions a {
        min-height: 48px;
        padding: 0.65rem 1.05rem;
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        border: 1px solid rgba(225, 205, 126, 0.24);
        color: #eee8d3;
        font-family: "Archivo Variable", "Atkinson", sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.7rem;
        font-weight: 680;
        letter-spacing: 0.06em;
        text-decoration: none;
        text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .manifesto-actions .manifesto-primary {
        border-color: #d3ad37;
        color: #102219;
        background: #d3ad37;
    }

    .manifesto-actions a:hover,
    .manifesto-actions a:focus-visible {
        border-color: #ead05d;
        outline: none;
    }

    .manifesto-actions .manifesto-primary:hover,
    .manifesto-actions .manifesto-primary:focus-visible {
        background: #e5c44f;
    }

    @media (max-width: 880px) {
        .archive-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .archive-card {
            grid-template-columns: minmax(220px, 0.8fr) 1fr;
            grid-template-rows: 1fr;
        }

        .card-media {
            aspect-ratio: 1;
        }

        .manifesto-orbit {
            opacity: 0.5;
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 680px) {
        .archive-shell,
        .manifesto-shell {
            width: calc(100% - 2rem);
        }

        .archive-header,
        .manifesto-layout {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: 1.4rem;
        }

        .archive-header h2,
        .manifesto h2 {
            font-size: clamp(2.75rem, 13vw, 4.25rem);
        }

        .archive-grid {
            display: grid;
        }

        .archive-card {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            grid-template-rows: auto 1fr;
        }

        .card-media {
            aspect-ratio: 16 / 10;
        }

        .manifesto-orbit {
            top: 14%;
            right: -28%;
            width: 90vw;
        }

        .manifesto-actions {
            display: grid;
        }
    }

    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
        .archive-card,
        .card-media img,
        .card-link b,
        .archive-intro a span {
            transition: none;
        }
    }
</style>
